Package: StatsSummary
Type: Package
Title: Quickly Calculate Descriptive Statistics for Clinical Trials
Version: 1.3.0
Author: Pedro Henrique Theotonio de Mesquita Pacheco
Maintainer: Pedro Henrique Theotonio de Mesquita Pacheco <pedrohmp36@gmail.com>
Description: StatsSummary is an R package focused on simplifying the rapid calculation of
   measures in clinical trials and statistical analyses. It allows users to easily generate statistics,
   optimizing time spent on repetitive tasks and ensuring accurate results ready for
   inclusion in reports and scientific publications.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    readr,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    tidyr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
